{"tid":2061039,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法庭拒絕黎智英取消禁止離境申請","createTime":"2020-06-12T05:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T12:20:15.000Z","uid":60281,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a36ca793ed4e2cbfd315462064219fa34b8491b","tid":2061039,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英因3年前涉嫌刑事恐嚇，及組織和參與去年3場未經批准的集結被起訴。黎智英涉及4宗案件，共獲准以7000元保釋候訊，期間不得離開香港及不得騷擾控方證人。他今早到高等法院申請更改保釋條件，提出取消禁止離境的要求，但遭法官拒絕申請，擇日頒布書面判詞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531633-20200612.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531633-20200612.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjDJoBOSHi9wRld7hxL8G3jc%3D&h=c173cff1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531633-20200612.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=42f786ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531633-20200612.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"93f9f5018d601d6620a86125bc2f94bf05007423","tid":2061039,"uid":45373,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:57:50.000Z","msg":"triple negative 睇左幾次先明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e0662b5e2bb9e68b6780a0cdccf636abe08f42","tid":2061039,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93f9f5018d601d6620a86125bc2f94bf05007423","tid":2061039,"uid":45373,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:57:50.000Z","msg":"triple negative 睇左幾次先明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:59:02.000Z","msg":"有無四重？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0d66dd2e1733fcc6ad7f988bb51fa9314c3608","tid":2061039,"uid":25771